PN,30501
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775581553
OL,3,CNew blood test to detect womb cancer
OL,4,Cin 48 hours
OL,6,FMedical breakthroughs often happen in
OL,7,Funexpected parts of the country.
OL,9,FBut when I meet Doctor Esther Moss in
OL,10,Fone of the many buildings that make up
OL,11,FLeicester Royal Infirmary, I am
OL,12,Fsurprised how she seems to downplay
OL,13,Fthis latest finding.
OL,15,F"It's a whole team effort," she tells
OL,16,Fme.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775581553
OL,3,CNew blood test to detect womb cancer
OL,4,Cin 48 hours
OL,6,FWe walk into a small unassuming
OL,7,Fgynaecology clinic room. There at the
OL,8,Fback of the room, I see the chair
OL,9,Fthat, I've been told, most patients
OL,10,Fdread. The gynae chair.
OL,12,FDr Moss made it her mission eight
OL,13,Fyears ago to come up with a test for
OL,14,Fher patients who were worried their
OL,15,Fendometrial cancer had returned post
OL,16,Ftreatment.
OL,18,F"Many patients find speculum and
OL,19,Fpelvic examination very challenging at
OL,20,Fthe best of times, let alone after
OL,21,Fcancer surgery," she says.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775581553
OL,3,CNew blood test to detect womb cancer
OL,4,Cin 48 hours
OL,6,FThe ECctDNA test, which looks for
OL,7,Ffragments of cancer in patients'
OL,8,Fblood, makes it easier and far less
OL,9,Finvasive to detect whether cancer has
OL,10,Frecurred, removing the need for
OL,11,Fpatients to have to undergo invasive
OL,12,Fphysical examinations, scans and
OL,13,Fpotentially uncomfortable biopsies.
OL,15,FExperts at the University of Leicester
OL,16,Fand University Hospitals of Leicester
OL,17,FNHS Trust have developed the test as
OL,18,Fpart of a study which recruited more
OL,19,Fthan 85 women with endometrial cancer
OL,20,Fwho were receiving treatment at the
OL,21,FLeicester Royal Infirmary.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775581553
OL,3,CNew blood test to detect womb cancer
OL,4,Cin 48 hours
OL,6,FEndometrial cancer, or womb cancer as
OL,7,Fit is also known, starts in the lining
OL,8,Fof the uterus (womb), called the
OL,9,Fendometrium.
OL,11,FIt is now the fourth most common
OL,12,Fcancer in women with around 9,800
OL,13,Fwomen diagnosed in the UK every year.
OL,15,F"We have been able to develop a blood
OL,16,Ftest that can not only diagnose womb
OL,17,Fcancer recurrence more quickly but can
OL,18,Favoid the need for confirmatory
OL,19,Finvasive biopsies," Dr Moss says.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775581553
OL,3,CNew blood test to detect womb cancer
OL,4,Cin 48 hours
OL,6,F"It can also give important
OL,7,Finformation to the clinical team on
OL,8,Fthe genetic changes that are driving
OL,9,Fthe cancer to recur, which could be
OL,10,Fused to guide patients' further
OL,11,Ftreatment'".
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FThe blood test nearly didn't happen.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775581553
OL,3,CNew blood test to detect womb cancer
OL,4,Cin 48 hours
OL,6,FDuring Covid, when the trial was at an
OL,7,Factive stage, all follow up
OL,8,Fappointments became telephone
OL,9,Fappointment and so it was difficult to
OL,10,Fcollect the blood samples from
OL,11,Fpatients.
OL,13,FGillian Stacey, 80 from Leicester, was
OL,14,Famong those who took part in the study.
OL,16,FShe was diagnosed with endometrial
OL,17,Fcancer 11 years ago after experiencing
OL,18,Funexpected bleeding.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775581553
OL,3,CNew blood test to detect womb cancer
OL,4,Cin 48 hours
OL,6,FHer womb was removed by the
OL,7,Fgynaecological oncology team in
OL,8,FLeicester and she received follow-up
OL,9,Fchemotherapy, radiotherapy and
OL,10,Fbrachytherapy.
OL,12,FGillian says her initial diagnosis of
OL,13,Flong-term survival was given as six
OL,14,Fmonths but she is still here fighting,
OL,15,Feven after developing cancer
OL,16,Frecurrence in the lungs five years
OL,17,Flater.
OL,19,FShe also takes a hormonal cancer
OL,20,Ftherapy drug and says: "I owe my life
OL,21,Fto Dr Esther Moss."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775581553
OL,3,CNew blood test to detect womb cancer
OL,4,Cin 48 hours
OL,6,F"I've had many medical examinations
OL,7,Fover the years and it can be
OL,8,Fincredibly invasive," Gillian says.
OL,10,F"You go through it and you do what you
OL,11,Fhave to do, but if there's an easier
OL,12,Fand less traumatic way to diagnose
OL,13,Fthis type of cancer then that would be
OL,14,Fa wonderful thing."
OL,16,FDr Moss tells us the rationale for
OL,17,Fdeveloping a blood test is that it can
OL,18,Fdeliver a result within 48 hours which
OL,19,Fis far quicker and more cost-effective
OL,20,Fthan a biopsy or internal examination.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775581553
OL,3,CNew blood test to detect womb cancer
OL,4,Cin 48 hours
OL,6,FAt the hospital, I meet Pippa
OL,7,FClarkson, a now retired fashion buyer
OL,8,Ffrom Leicestershire. She was diagnosed
OL,9,Fwith womb cancer after noticing she
OL,10,Fwas bleeding after the menopause.
OL,12,F"I went through that at 52, I'm 57 at
OL,13,Fthis point," she tells me.
OL,15,F"I had quite a lot of internal
OL,16,Fexaminations ... they are undignified
OL,17,Fand it's also not always with a lady
OL,18,Fdoctor. That was always stressing me
OL,19,Fout a bit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775581553
OL,3,CNew blood test to detect womb cancer
OL,4,Cin 48 hours
OL,6,F"I always wanted a female doctor but
OL,7,Fyou can't guarantee it. It's just
OL,8,Fsomething you have to build yourself
OL,9,Fup for. I didn't find it particularly
OL,10,Fpainful but some people do."
OL,12,FAfter having surgery to remove her
OL,13,Fwomb, Pippa had a short course of
OL,14,Ffollow up treatment before opting for
OL,15,Ffive years of review to ensure the
OL,16,Fcancer didn't come back. That's when
OL,17,Fshe was recruited to Dr Moss' study.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775581553
OL,3,CNew blood test to detect womb cancer
OL,4,Cin 48 hours
OL,6,F"At that point, I was approached by
OL,7,Fthe team and asked if I'd be prepared
OL,8,Fto take part in this trial. And
OL,9,Fobviously I said yes because I wanted
OL,10,Fto give something back," she says.
OL,12,F"It's a bit of a no-brainer really but
OL,13,FI don't think I had any idea just how
OL,14,Fimportant at that point in time it was
OL,15,Factually going to be."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775581553
OL,3,CNew blood test to detect womb cancer
OL,4,Cin 48 hours
OL,6,FDr Moss and other scientists at the
OL,7,FUniversity Hospitals of Leicester's
OL,8,FNIHR Biomedical Research Centre and
OL,9,FUniversity of Leicester are now
OL,10,Fworking on the additional validation
OL,11,Fand quality control needed to allow
OL,12,Fthe test to be used across the NHS.
OL,14,FIt's expected the new blood test to
OL,15,Fdetect endometrial cancer recurrence
OL,16,Fwill be common practice in NHS
OL,17,Fhospitals by 2028.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
